{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Introduction</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Excidio the Kaiju Simulator invites you to immerse yourself as a massive kaiju and lay waste to fully destructible physics-based environments at your leisure. Topple familiar landmarks and take on the military and other Kaiju that dare threaten you.  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Play as a Kaiju!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Immerse yourself as one of three unique kaiju, Excidio, Golem or Raijin!  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Physics-based destruction</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fully physics-based realistic destruction. Walk through buildings only leaving rubble behind. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Unique maps</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play on a variety of unique maps inspired by real locations! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Game Modes!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play Arcade mode, upgrade your kaiju as you try and survive the onslaught of constant enemies. Or play your way in Sandbox! Featuring a variety of customizable options for you to do as you please. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">PvE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Face off against the military and enemy Kaiju as they try to stop your path of destruction! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Photo modes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use a variety of photo modes and filters to capture screenshots and see the destruction from unique perspectives! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Crossovers</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dawn of the Monsters TM and \u00a92023 13AM Games, Megadon\u00a9 2023 13AM Games, Inc. All rights reserved. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Terror of Hemasaurus Copyright 2024 Games By Loren.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Primatus Rex created by Dangerville.</p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Beginning of the End","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1594130/70e12b1848ebccf046e4ee057fce8a538d448467.jpg"},{"name":"Redeemed","path":"https://cdn.akamai.st